  25 Feb 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r3.ebuild,
  flaggie-9999.ebuild:
  Add ~ppc64 per bug #459194.

  17 Dec 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild,
  flaggie-0.2-r3.ebuild, flaggie-9999.ebuild:
  Bump to EAPI=5 to make Paludis happy, bug #447524.

  16 Dec 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #445178

*flaggie-9999 (15 Dec 2012)

  15 Dec 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-9999.ebuild:
  Import the live ebuild.

*flaggie-0.2-r3 (09 Dec 2012)

  09 Dec 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Enable python3.3 and pypy1.8.

  02 Dec 2012; <ago@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #445178

  29 Nov 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Remove pypy from PYTHON_COMPAT to clear the path for STABLEREQ.

  29 Nov 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  22 Nov 2012; Ian Delaney <idella4@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  pypy comaptibility added

  21 Oct 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Re-add ~x86-fbsd & ~amd64-fbsd after keywording python-exec.

  20 Oct 2012; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #438388).

  16 Oct 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Re-keyword ~arm for python-exec being keyworded.

*flaggie-0.2-r2 (15 Oct 2012)

  15 Oct 2012; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Revision bump to distutils-r1.

