*flaggie-0.2 (17 Dec 2011)

  17 Dec 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.2.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump. The new version always aborts on ambiguous atoms and brings
  updated bash-completion.

  09 Dec 2011; Naohiro Aota <naota@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd #393175

  02 Nov 2011; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #345441

  01 Nov 2011; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Marked stable on AMD64 based on arch testing by Agostino "ago" Sarubbo & Ian
  "idella4" Delaney in bug #345441.

  26 Oct 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Restrict Python 3 due to bugs in it.

  16 Oct 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Migrate to bash-completion-r1.

*flaggie-0.1.4 (08 Oct 2011)

  08 Oct 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.1.3.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version fixes issue writing new USE variable.

*flaggie-0.1.3 (30 Aug 2011)

  30 Aug 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.4.ebuild,
  -flaggie-0.1.2.ebuild, +flaggie-0.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version fixes support for invalid USE_EXPAND values
  (bug #380505) and -env:: action (bug #372069).

*flaggie-0.1.2 (14 Aug 2011)

  14 Aug 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.1.1.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.1.2.ebuild:
  Long-delayed version bump to 0.1.2 bugfix.

*flaggie-0.1.1 (19 Jan 2011)

  19 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.1.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.1.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version fixes treating license groups as incorrect args
  and adds support for USE_EXPAND variables in make.conf.

  16 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.0.4.ebuild,
  flaggie-0.1.ebuild:
  Add missing app-shells/gentoo-bashcomp RDEP for bash-completion. Thanks to
  Jacek Sowiński.

*flaggie-0.1 (15 Jan 2011)

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version introduces preliminary support for global
  (make.conf) actions.

  08 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.0.4.ebuild:
  Use bash-completion.eclass.

*flaggie-0.0.4 (07 Jan 2011)

  07 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.0.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fixes #349108 (package.accept_keywords support) and #349207
  ('*' special keyword), adds a bash-completion script.

  06 Jan 2011; Dane Smith <c1pher@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild:
  Tested on arm. Marking ~arm.

  05 Jan 2011; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.2.4.ebuild,
  flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild:
  EAPI bump, drop old version.

  20 Dec 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.0.2.4.ebuild,
  flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild:
  Change the SRC_URIs to use cloud.github.com directly. This avoids issues with
  (pointless) SSL and old wget versions.

  19 Dec 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> flaggie-0.0.2.4.ebuild,
  flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild:
  Clarify the Portage RDEP.

  19 Dec 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Clarify the <bugs-to/> URL.

*flaggie-0.0.3 (08 Dec 2010)

  08 Dec 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.2.3.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.0.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version introduces package.env file support and further
  bugfixes.

*flaggie-0.0.2.4 (23 Nov 2010)

  23 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.0.2.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version fixes '**' keyword argument support and uses
  atomic writes.

*flaggie-0.0.2.3 (17 Nov 2010)

  17 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.2.2.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.0.2.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fixes crash with non-existent files and auto-shortening
  unmodified package.keywords entries.

*flaggie-0.0.2.2 (15 Nov 2010)

  15 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.2.1.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.0.2.2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump, with important bugfixes (whitespace problems, omitting
  backup files).

*flaggie-0.0.2.1 (13 Nov 2010)

  13 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.2.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.0.2.1.ebuild:
  Version bump, fixing issues with shortcut package.keywords entries.

*flaggie-0.0.2 (10 Nov 2010)

  10 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -flaggie-0.0.1.ebuild,
  +flaggie-0.0.2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Version bump. The new version fixes important runtime issues, and supplies
  a few new cleanup actions. Fixing typos in metadata.xml too.

*flaggie-0.0.1 (07 Nov 2010)

  07 Nov 2010; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +flaggie-0.0.1.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  Introducing flaggie, a new CLI package.* file mangler.
